snippet.title: The Golf Club Collector's Edition - Master Your Game :30
snippet.description:
Create gorgeous, custom-designed courses, then share online with other players across multiple platforms.  Award winning game now has these NEW features:
Season Mode with five tour levels of advancement.
Tropical elements to create lush resort courses.
BONUS Collectible e-Book for real golf enthusiasts.
